citations:
    citation-affc-cat-of-the-canals-i:
        source: source-affc
        properties:
            locator: "Cat of the Canals"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Arya Stark, now trained at the House of Black and White in Braavos, works as 'Cat of the Canals' — a fish-seller's girl. She kills Dareon, the Night's Watch deserter and singer, by drowning him in a canal after he deserts his oath and gives away the black cloak. The Kindly Man is displeased but notes she has kept her oath. Arya then wakes blind — the Kindly Man's punishment for killing without the god's sanction."
